<HEADLINE> Namibian Premier Calls on Mugabe </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HARARE, June 13 (Xinhua) -- Namibian Prime Minister Hage
Gaigab, who is in Zimbabwe for a one-week state visit, today met
with Zimbabwean president Robert Mugabe.
</P>
<P>
