president Sam Nujoma to stand for reelection.
</P>
<P>
Nujoma was unanimously chosen by Swapo congress this year to
be the party's candidate for a third term. The constitution
allows a president to run for two terms only.
</P>
<P>
Mugabe said Gaigab's visit would help consolidate the
relationship between the two countries, and enable them share
ideas on important issues and the re-distribution of national
resources. 
