United Nations Mission of Observer to Tajikistan from January 1993
to March 1995, Senior Advisor to the Special Representative of the
Secretary-General on Somalia from May to December 1992, and
Director and Senior Advisor to the Under-Secretary-General for
Human Rights in Geneva from 1988 to 1992. 
