journalists today that the venue with only two percent of the
construction work still remaining, is expected to mitigate
scarcity of recreation centers in the capital.
</P>
<P>
She said a ten-day fund raising program will be launched
beginning from June 20 with a view to furnish the amphitheatre
with the necessary facilities.
</P>
<P>
Beginning next September, theatres, circus, festivals, films
and sports events will be staged at the amphitheatre, according
to the head. 
