<HEADLINE> Germany Grants 3 Million Dollars to Tanzania </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DAR ES SALAAM, June 14 (Xinhua) -- Tanzania and Germany early
this week signed an agreement, under which Germany will grant
Tanzania 4.97 billion Tanzania Shillings (about 3.016 million US
Dollars) to implement different projects.
</P>
<P>
According to a press release issued by the Treasury here on
Friday, the grant will help promotion of crafts and small scale
trades, science teaching in secondary schools and vocational
training.
</P>
<P>
