notes with Principal Secretary in the Ministry of Finance,
Raphael Mollel, said the fund for promotion crafts and
small-scale trades would help self-help groups in all trades of
the informal sector in the Tanzanian capital.
</P>
<P>
He said the fund for promotion of science teaching in
secondary schools was aimed at improving teaching and learning
facilities in schools.
</P>
<P>
On vocational education and training, the ambassador said the
project aimed at strengthening the role of Vocational Education
and Training (VETA) as a facilitator and co-ordinator of
vocational education training system in the country. 
